{"tid":186100,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"家中發現依種蟲，求教係乜","createTime":"2017-04-04T03:32:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-04T03:52:49.000Z","uid":75985,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"610169a98a81e66a91e41074e9420d60caec941c","tid":186100,"uid":75985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T03:32:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/supaylj4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fsupaylj4&h=c5a941eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n尋晚陸續發現五、六隻，掃走或殺蟲水殺死，奇怪點解無端端出現，搞掂一隻冇耐又見一隻咁，後尾搵搵下見到枕頭套近開口的內側有堆青白色圓形粒粒，已爆開一大半，諗多諗就醒覺係卵，即刻成個枕頭都唔要兼噴殺蟲水，都唔敢睇內裡有乜喇。<br />\n<br />\n想確認下係咪咩臭屁蟲幼蟲？"},{"pid":"515c1ce28105408cf001f79ab46a9b9dae2268e1","tid":186100,"uid":9557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T03:33:01.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"111dfed9f6e126106274fc41449a6fd91698fb14","tid":186100,"uid":91236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T03:34:18.000Z","msg":"點解係枕頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e8b2331666771e603c84075787e415b050c89f0","tid":186100,"uid":53126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T03:36:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解係枕頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n枕頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a8881c9fe82990a3a6bbb0233555b521e1007bd","tid":186100,"uid":21394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T03:38:05.000Z","msg":"咪整死，先人來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"167a7e023f04b0e06bea7ae33e1dcc65b5f45cb3","tid":186100,"uid":24682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T03:39: